*Great Belt Power Link — &quot;electrical power cable&quot;.
*Danish Straits — &quot;includes Great Belt&quot;.
**Little Belt — &quot;strait between Jutland and Funen&quot;.
**Øresund — &quot;strait between Zealand and Sweden&quot;.
*March across the Belts

